# SalesBOT Mobile Application (v1.0.0) - Android & iOS Package

Welcome to SalesBOT (ShopBot AI) Mobile!
This application is built using Expo SDK 57 and React Native 0.86.

## Cross-Platform Compatibility:
- Android: Fully compatible (Package: com.salesbot.ai, Permissions: RECORD_AUDIO for voice search)
- iOS: Fully compatible (Bundle ID: com.salesbot.ai, Info.plist: NSMicrophoneUsageDescription for voice search)

## How to Install & Build Native APK / IPA:

1. Local Development / Expo Go:
   - Run `cd mobile && npm install`
   - Run `npx expo start`
   - Scan the QR code using the Expo Go app on your Android or iOS device!

2. Build Native Android APK (Release):
   - Ensure Android Studio / Android SDK is installed.
   - Run `npx expo run:android --variant release` or use EAS Build: `eas build -p android --profile preview`.
   - The resulting standalone APK can be directly installed on any Android smartphone!

3. Build Native iOS IPA (Release):
   - On macOS with Xcode installed, run `npx expo run:ios --configuration Release` or use EAS Build: `eas build -p ios`.

Enjoy live multi-store comparison shopping across Amazon, Flipkart, Croma, Reliance Digital, and Vijay Sales!
